\end{equation*}


where $\left(x_{0}(t), \gamma\right)(a)=\gamma\left(\operatorname{Ad}\left(x_{0}(-t)\right) a\right)$ for any a $\varepsilon N$.\\
Moreover, if tensor product maps to multiplication, one has an isomorphism


